<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bootstrap 4 Carousel</title>
    <!-- Include Bootstrap CSS from a CDN -->
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Style for images within cards to ensure they fit well */
        .card-img-top {
            max-width: 100%; /* Ensures image scales with card width */
            height: auto; /* Maintains aspect ratio */
            max-height: 200px; /* Sets a maximum height for the image */
            object-fit: contain; /* Ensures the image is contained within the specified dimensions */
        }

        /* Style for the card component */
        .card {
            background-color: #8D493A; /* Background color for cards */
            color: #FFFFFF; /* Text color for cards */
            font-family: 'Raleway', serif; /* Font family for card text */
        }

        /* Style for card header and body */
        .card-header, .card-body {
            background-color: #8D493A; /* Background color */
            color: #FFFFFF; /* Text color */
            font-family: 'Raleway', serif; /* Font family */
        }

        /* Style for buttons */
        .btn {
            color: #FFFFFF; /* Text color for buttons */
            font-family: 'Raleway', serif; /* Font family */
        }

        /* Style for images within the carousel */
        .carousel-item img {
            width: 100%; /* Full width of the carousel item */
            height: auto; /* Maintains aspect ratio */
            object-fit: cover; /* Ensures image covers the container while maintaining aspect ratio */
        }

        /* Style for the card container to add spacing */
        .card-container {
            margin-bottom: 30px; /* Adjust this value for more space between cards */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-3">
        <!-- Main heading -->
        <br />
        <h2 style="text-align: center;">Welcome!</h2>
        <h3 style="text-align: center;">Dive deep into the world of Mutual Funds!</h3>
        <br />
        <h4>Collections</h4>
        <br />

        <div class="row">
            <!-- Card 1: Large Cap -->
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex justify-content-center card-container">
                <a href="/MutualFund/Index?category=LargeCap" class="card text-decoration-none" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img src="images/large-cap.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="Large Cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Large Cap</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Stability meets scale – start investing in industry giants.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2: Mid Cap -->
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex justify-content-center card-container">
                <a href="/MutualFund/Index?category=MidCap" class="card text-decoration-none" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img src="images/mid-cap.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="Mid Cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Mid Cap</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Growth in motion – capture the sweet spot of expansion.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3: Small Cap -->
            <div class="col-md-4 d-flex justify-content-center card-container">
                <a href="/MutualFund/Index?category=SmallCap" class="card text-decoration-none" style="width: 18rem;">
                    <img src="images/small-cap.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="Small Cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Small Cap</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">High potential, high reward – dive into emerging stars.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Carousel for displaying images -->
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide mt-5" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <!-- Carousel indicators for navigation -->
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <!-- First slide -->
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="https://www.investsmall.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/fin-investment-1024x683.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 1">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <!-- Caption content (currently empty) -->
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Second slide -->
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://berganco.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/rental-property-investment-strategy-1110x624.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 2">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <!-- Caption content (currently empty) -->
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Third slide -->
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/mortgage-home-loan-interest-rate-concept-taxes-generative-ai_887552-13884.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 3">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                        <!-- Caption content (currently empty) -->
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Carousel controls for previous and next -->
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ section with accordion -->
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h4>FAQ</h4>
            <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                <!-- FAQ 1 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                What is a mutual fund?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            A mutual fund is an investment vehicle that pools together money from many investors to purchase securities. Each investor owns shares in the fund, which represents a portion of the holdings.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 2 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                What are the benefits of investing in mutual funds?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            Mutual funds offer diversification, professional management, and liquidity. They allow investors to own a mix of securities, reducing the risk compared to investing in individual stocks.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 3 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingThree">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                How are mutual funds taxed?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            Mutual funds are subject to capital gains taxes. Short-term capital gains (from investments held for less than a year) are taxed at the investor’s ordinary income tax rate, while long-term capital gains (from investments held for more than a year) are taxed at a lower rate.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 4 -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">
                            <button class="btn" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                How do I choose a mutual fund?
                            </button>
                        </h5>
                    </div>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            When choosing a mutual fund, consider factors like your investment goals, risk tolerance, fund performance, and fees. It’s also helpful to review the fund’s prospectus and consult with a financial advisor.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include Bootstrap JS and its dependencies -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
